                  <additions>
                     
                     
                     
                     <p>Folio 39 is a small parchment leaf inserted into the codex and it contains a get delivered by Eliezer ben Isaac Ashkenazi to his wife Fiorita bat Yehoshua, dated 5330 (1570). </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     <p>Folio 56 is a small paper leaf inserted into the codex and it contains on one side the record of some derushim, and on the other side part of a piece on Yom Kipur. </p>
                  
                  
                  
